data.description: Spacious 3 bed, 2 full bath home w/ FROG in amenity-rich, water-access, and gated community Mimosa Bay!  Built in 2018 as the model, this home has it all: open concept, split floor plan, formal dining room, gas fireplace, granite counters, stainless appliances, rear covered patio, nice back yard, and spacious downstairs master suite.  Talk about location, location, location - only 5 minutes to the sand at North Topsail.  Community features a pool, tennis courts, boat & RV storage, as well as a boat ramp and pier.  It's the perfect place to soak up the sun and take in the natural beauty of coastal NC.
